Package dynRDFa

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DynRDFa
    Driver class.
    ExportableModel
    The ExportableModel class packs together all the information that the velocity engine and template need to consume in order to generate the RDFa enriched web pages.
    ModelMaker
    The purpose of the ModelMaker class is to provide methods that transform a relational (mySQL) database to structures that can be utilized to generate RDFa enriched web pages.
    QueryReader
    The class parses a text file with a set of queries in it and then provides a way to hash into the set of queries using a name identifier.
    Treeple
    The Treeple class groups together statements that share the same subject.
    VelociDataModel
    The VelociDataModel class serves as the go-between for application and template.
